{"word":"H7080 - קָסַם - qâçam - kaw-sam' - Divine","slug":"H7080","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קָסַם</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>qâçam"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kaw-sam'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Divine"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E7;&#x05E1;&#x05DD; - qa&#x0302;sam</b> - <i>kaw-sam'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>distribute</i>, that is, <i>determine</i> by lot or magical scroll; by implication to <i>divine: - </i>divine (-r, -ation), prudent, soothsayer, use [divination]."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4738\">H4738</a>, <a href=\"#/H7081\">H7081</a>"}]}